" by embedding content (i.e., videos, photo albums, music play lists, calendars, etc.) from many divergent sources and presenting them in a useful, accessible and personalized manner. Spinlets are completely based on browser technologies such as <format wordnetid="106636806" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../191/13191.xml">
